title: [Winterchime's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a swirl-painted white stucco ceiling, a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin hangs on one of the painted white plaster walls.  A glass-topped mistwood counter and a white marble shelf sit in opposite corners while a woven Vornavian silk rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.

Beneath a swirl-painted white stucco ceiling, a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin hangs on one of the painted white plaster walls.  A glass-topped mistwood counter and a white marble shelf sit in opposite corners while a beautiful blue sapphire-inlaid music stand holding an ancient volume of harp music rests on a gold-speckled marble floor.
